- Power-obsessed: will challenge anyone at any rank, any time
- Crosses the line into insanity — first occurrence: walked directly into grandmaster-level fighters as an intermediate newbie to challenge for King
- Second occurrence: challenged all three houses (Spade, Diamond, Heart) simultaneously to satisfy his hunger for battle with queens, aces, jokers — everyone except the Kings in his "Lvl 3 range" and his own 12 of Clubs

---

## Power Levels

- **First mortal to pass "Storm of Changes"** (domain/power test equivalent)
- **Lvl 1:** Change of Storm — raw power burst
- **Lvl 2:** TBD
- **Lvl 3:** Domain — exact form not yet defined

---

## Arc

- **Start:** Intermediate newbie, insane enough to challenge upward
- **Rise:** Passes Storm of Changes (unprecedented); earns King of Clubs
- **Story present:** Challenging across all houses; the spine of the Lvl 1 arc

---

